<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA55">
<l>maruṅkōta mōtu maṇinā kaṇaiyār</l>
<l>maruṅkē varavariya rēlu moruṅkē</l>
<l>yemakkavaraik kāṇalā meppōtu muḷḷāṉ</l>
<l>maṉakkavalai tīrppār varavu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though it is difficult to come to the side of him</l>
<l>whose bed is a sapphire snake where the flood whispers on the side,</l>
<l>together for us there is always seeing him with the mind,</l>
<l>the coming of him wo ends the sorrows of the mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
